   1              	/*
   2              	 *  @File        bootmiddle.S
   3              	 *  @Brief       The Second boot section of Sodex
   4              	 *  @Description This section mainly consist of changing from 16bit mode to
   5              	 *               32bit mode and setting other CPU's something ought to be.
